text:

Dance ka passion koi siikhe inse, siikhe inse!
Poore chaar saal me tu parties se door raha, lekin end me hmare level pe gira hi diya humneğŸ» Tere se hi hasna aur bartender ka asli matlab siikha hai humne! Aage bhi milte rhna aur party krte rhna hmare saath.
Horror movies toh ab US me hi complete krenge. Waiting for you in HawaiiğŸ¹

text:
Yo Ranjan!
Bhai, party king ka asli matlab tu nibhaata hai! Jitne bhi parties ki hain maine campus me, teri wajah se hi hui hain. Jab se double room liya hai, hmara adda tera room hi rha hai. Tere room me itne maze ki hain ki kya bataaoon! Games khelne aur dekhne se leke IPL matches dekhne tak, sab normal maze kiye hain. Phir khaliğŸ˜‚ aur bhariğŸ˜­ bottles thodne se leke fire extinguisher chalane tak bhi extreme maze kiye hain!

text:
Yo Bhagat bro!
First year me class samay Mini militia khelne se leke aakhri mahine me party karne tak, poore chaar saal time spend kiya hai humne. Kahan student lounge padne jaate the, par pubg khelke wapas lautte theğŸ˜‚
Library me couples se pareshaan hoke lautna aur fest samay events ground pe jalna, kabhi nhi bhul paaoonga maiğŸ˜­
Gaming me introduction tune hi diya hai mere ko, aur yhi sabse best moments create kiye hain! Der raat tak tere ko games khelte dekhna aur saath me khelna, one of the best moments hain mere
